nal plasma, and smaller X-ray flares. The\nimpulsive SEP events do not come from hot flare plasma; they are accelerated\nearly and/or on adjacent open field lines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Jan 2015 21:57:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-06"}
