quences of\nthese findings for our understanding of the structure of the Milky Way disc.\nBecause the Sun is situated slightly outside the OLR, we suggest that the solar\nvicinity may have experienced very limited churning from the inner disc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Jan 2015 10:56:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 May 2015 17:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-10"}
